# Backend Rule

- Keep backend flow modular: Module -> Controller/Gateway -> Service -> Repository.
- Keep business logic out of controllers and gateways; place it in services.
- Use strict TypeScript with explicit DTO validation; avoid `any`.
- Use semantic exceptions and consistent status codes aligned with API contracts.
- Add or update tests when behavior changes; prefer test-first changes.
